		MESSAGE
		{
			title = World First Milestones
			message = The recent accomplishments of our space program have attracted contributions from numerous organizations!~n~nWe have performed the first one of our experiments at home.~n<color=#b4d455><sprite="CurrencySpriteAsset" name="Funds" tint=1> 1,600 </color>~n~n We have launched our first vessel.~n <color=#b4d455><sprite="CurrencySpriteAsset" name="Funds" tint=1>  800 </color>~n~n We have broken a speed record of 25m/s.~n <color=#b4d455><sprite="CurrencySpriteAsset" name="Funds" tint=1>  4,800 </color>~n~n We have broken a speed record of 80m/s.~n <color=#b4d455><sprite="CurrencySpriteAsset" name="Funds" tint=1>  4,800 </color><color=#e0d503><sprite="CurrencySpriteAsset" name="Reputation" tint=1> 1 </color>~n~n We have broken an altitude record of 500m.~n <color=#b4d455><sprite="CurrencySpriteAsset" name="Funds" tint=1>  4,800 </color>~n~n We have broken an altitude record of 2,000m.~n <color=#b4d455><sprite="CurrencySpriteAsset" name="Funds" tint=1>  4,800 </color><color=#e0d503><sprite="CurrencySpriteAsset" name="Reputation" tint=1> 1 </color>~n~n We have broken a speed record of 250m/s.~n <color=#b4d455><sprite="CurrencySpriteAsset" name="Funds" tint=1>  4,800 </color>~n~n We have broken an altitude record of 7,000m.~n <color=#b4d455><sprite="CurrencySpriteAsset" name="Funds" tint=1>  4,800 </color>~n~n We have broken a land distance record of 1,000m.~n <color=#b4d455><sprite="CurrencySpriteAsset" name="Funds" tint=1>  4,800 </color>~n~n We have broken a land distance record of 3,000m.~n <color=#b4d455><sprite="CurrencySpriteAsset" name="Funds" tint=1>  4,800 </color><color=#e0d503><sprite="CurrencySpriteAsset" name="Reputation" tint=1> 1 </color>~n~n We have splashed into the ocean.~n <color=#b4d455><sprite="CurrencySpriteAsset" name="Funds" tint=1>  2,400 </color>~n~n We have broken a speed record of 790m/s.~n <color=#b4d455><sprite="CurrencySpriteAsset" name="Funds" tint=1>  4,800 </color><color=#e0d503><sprite="CurrencySpriteAsset" name="Reputation" tint=1> 1 </color>~n~n We have broken an altitude record of 22km.~n <color=#b4d455><sprite="CurrencySpriteAsset" name="Funds" tint=1>  4,800 </color><color=#e0d503><sprite="CurrencySpriteAsset" name="Reputation" tint=1> 1 </color>~n~n We have broken a land distance record of 10km.~n <color=#b4d455><sprite="CurrencySpriteAsset" name="Funds" tint=1>  4,800 </color>~n~n We have broken an altitude record of 70km.~n <color=#b4d455><sprite="CurrencySpriteAsset" name="Funds" tint=1>  4,800 </color><color=#6dcff6><sprite="CurrencySpriteAsset" name="Science" tint=1> 1 </color><color=#e0d503><sprite="CurrencySpriteAsset" name="Reputation" tint=1> 1 </color>~n~n We have reached space.~n <color=#b4d455><sprite="CurrencySpriteAsset" name="Funds" tint=1>  8,000 </color><color=#e0d503><sprite="CurrencySpriteAsset" name="Reputation" tint=1> 1 </color>~n~n We have broken a land distance record of 32km.~n <color=#b4d455><sprite="CurrencySpriteAsset" name="Funds" tint=1>  4,800 </color><color=#e0d503><sprite="CurrencySpriteAsset" name="Reputation" tint=1> 1 </color>~n~n We have broken a land distance record of 100km.~n <color=#b4d455><sprite="CurrencySpriteAsset" name="Funds" tint=1>  4,800 </color><color=#6dcff6><sprite="CurrencySpriteAsset" name="Science" tint=1> 1 </color><color=#e0d503><sprite="CurrencySpriteAsset" name="Reputation" tint=1> 1 </color>~n~n We have returned to the surface.~n <color=#b4d455><sprite="CurrencySpriteAsset" name="Funds" tint=1>  800 </color>~n~n We have broken a speed record of 2,500m/s.~n <color=#b4d455><sprite="CurrencySpriteAsset" name="Funds" tint=1>  4,800 </color><color=#6dcff6><sprite="CurrencySpriteAsset" name="Science" tint=1> 1 </color><color=#e0d503><sprite="CurrencySpriteAsset" name="Reputation" tint=1> 1 </color>~n
			color = 3
